    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Liquidambar cambodiana are inflammation and diabetes, which are effectively treated due to its flavonoids and phenolic acids. The plant's anti-inflammatory and antioxidant properties also alleviate arthritis, a chronic condition characterized by joint pain and swelling. Studies have shown that Liquidambar cambodiana extracts exhibit vasodilatory effects, reducing blood pressure in individuals with hypertension, thus preventing cardiovascular disease. Liquidambar cambodiana has been proven to inhibit cancer cell proliferation by inducing apoptosis and preventing cell growth, and its anti-cancer properties have been validated in various studies. Additionally, the plant's extracts have been found to exhibit antibacterial activity, treating gastroenteritis, diarrhea, rheumatism, fever, gastritis, malaria, cough, skin irritation, respiratory issues, dysentery, influenza, infection, and wound infection.",
